{"tid":1331391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請正確教育深藍-愛國不等於愛黨","createTime":"2019-07-19T02:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T04:15:59.000Z","uid":176700,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"807facbbd7d68e12a127885b5869da75b11b342a","tid":1331391,"uid":176700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:25:14.000Z","msg":"好多深藍其中一個主要point,  就係之前中國點樣被外國入侵， 尤其抗日戰爭， 繼而討厭呢場運動。 <br />\n<br />\n請文宣組介紹香港民主元老---<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">司徒華(華叔)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n前香港總督彭定康對司徒華的評價︰「從來沒有人稱他是英國帝國的工具，他是一個反殖民地主義者，堅定、強硬及非常聰明的中國愛國主義者。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個愛中國， 希望建立民主中國ge人， 最後得到咩回報？就係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中國共匪回收佢ge回鄉證， 不停咁打壓佢</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一個政權， 唔能夠包容多元化聲音， 不停打壓異見人士， 點解要支持， 擁護？</span>"},{"pid":"47584e7e6375b07aca43246b3ec8f83599a0bb4c","tid":1331391,"uid":176700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:27:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f1ecbf1e0b8708e93e3fc0178c60e83b08372c6","tid":1331391,"uid":176700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:27:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4afd33a5ed410834673909a180a23428460d3f8c","tid":1331391,"uid":176700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:28:02.000Z","msg":"推。"},{"pid":"823d548fba0b9e9d5dd9fee4047a84906b2271ef","tid":1331391,"uid":176700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:28:12.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"05f72622681ef7f34e2c242fc4fbea978da69779","tid":1331391,"uid":176700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:29:19.000Z","msg":"推！！！！"},{"pid":"bafa143976a74fea0cdf1b05bc62796acf0bb5d8","tid":1331391,"uid":176700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T02:32:03.000Z","msg":"推！！！！"},{"pid":"9760939fdd65a51260cbe1a88f8aafb29c1a7554","tid":1331391,"uid":176700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201